<paragraph blockId="0.[1223,2106,1044,1243]" pageId="0" pageNumber="236">• Primary rainforests, secondary forests, and occasionally gardens.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1223,2106,1044,1243]" box="[1225,1646,1167,1196]" pageId="0" pageNumber="236">• 1 genus, 1 species, 2 taxa.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1223,2106,1044,1243]" box="[1225,1994,1202,1235]" pageId="0" pageNumber="236">• No species threatened; none Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
